\c 4
\s Inzalo kaJuda
\p
\v 1 Amadodana kaJuda\x + Gen. 38.29. 46.12.\x*: OPerezi, uHezironi, loKarmi, loHuri\x + 2.19.\x*, loShobhali\x + 2.50.\x*.
\v 2 UReyaya indodana kaShobhali wasezala uJahathi; uJahathi wasezala uAhumayi loLahadi. Laba babezinsendo zamaZorathi\x + 2.53,54.\x*.
\p
\v 3 Laba babengabakayise kaEtamu: OJizereyeli\x + Josh. 15.56.\x* loIshma loIdibhashi; lebizo likadadewabo lalinguHazeleliponi.
\v 4 LoPenuweli uyise kaGedori\x + 4.18,39.\x*, loEzeri uyise kaHusha. Laba babengamadodana kaHuri\x + 2.50.\x*, izibulo likaEfratha, uyise kaBhethelehema\x + 2.51.\x*.
\p
\v 5 Njalo uAshuri uyise kaThekhowa wayelabafazi ababili, oHela loNahara\x + 2.24.\x*.
\v 6 UNahara wasemzalela uAhuzama loHeferi loTemeni loHahashitari. Laba babengamadodana kaNahara.
\v 7 Lamadodana kaHela: OZerethi loIzohari loEthinani.
\v 8 UKhozi wasezala uAnubi loZobeba, lensendo zikaAhariheli indodana kaHarumi.
\p
\v 9 Njalo uJabezi\x + 2.55.\x* wayelodumo kulabafowabo\x + Gen. 34.19.\x*; unina wasemutha ibizo \add wathi\add* nguJabezi, esithi: Ngoba ngamzala ngisosizini\x + Gen. 3.16.\x*.
\v 10 UJabezi wasebiza uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli esithi: Kungathi ungangibusisa lokungibusisa, uqhelise umngcele wami, lesandla sakho sibe lami, ungivikele ebubini ukuze bungangidabuli! UNkulunkulu wenza kwenzakala lokho akucelayo.
\p
\v 11 UKelubi umfowabo kaShuha wasezala uMehiri, onguyise kaEshitoni.
\v 12 UEshitoni wasezala uBeti-Rafa loPhaseya loTehina uyise kaIri-Nahashi. Laba babengabantu bakaReka.
\v 13 Lamadodana kaKenazi\x + Josh. 15.17. Hlu. 1.13. 3.9,11.\x*: O-Othiniyeli\x + Josh. 15.17. Hlu. 1.13. 3.9,11.\x* loSeraya. Lamadodana kaOthiniyeli: UHathathi.
\v 14 UMeyonothayi wasezala uOfira. USeraya wasezala uJowabi uyise wesigodi seHarashi, ngoba babezingcitshi\x + Neh. 11.35.\x*.
\v 15 Lamadodana kaKalebi indodana kaJefune\x + Nani 13.6.\x*: OIru, uEla, loNahamu; lamadodana kaEla, ngitsho uKenazi.
\v 16 Lamadodana kaJehaleleli: OZifi, loZifa\x + 2.42.\x*, uTiriya, loAsareli.
\v 17 Lamadodana kaEzra: OJetheri loMeredi loEferi loJaloni. Wasezala oMiriyamu loShamayi loIshiba uyise kaEshithemowa\x + 4.19. 6.57.\x*.
\v 18 Umkakhe umJudakazi wasezala uJeredi uyise kaGedori\x + 4.4.\x*, loHeberi uyise kaSoko\x + Josh. 15.35.\x*, loJekuthiyeli uyise kaZanowa\x + Josh. 15.34.\x*. Lalabo babengamadodana kaBithiya indodakazi kaFaro, uMeredi amthathayo.
\v 19 Lamadodana omkaHodiya, udadewabo kaNahama, uyise kaKeyila umGarmi\x + 1 Sam. 23.1.\x*, loEshithemowa umMahakathi\x + 2 Sam. 10.6.\x*.
\v 20 Njalo amadodana kaShimoni: OAmnoni, loRina, uBheni-Hanani, loThiloni. Lamadodana kaIshi: OZohethi loBheni-Zohethi.
\p
\v 21 Amadodana kaShela indodana kaJuda\x + 2.3. 9.5. Gen. 38.1,5. 46.12. Nani 26.20. Neh. 11.5.\x*: OEri uyise kaLeka, loLahada uyise kaMaresha\x + 2.42.\x*, lensendo zendlu yabenzi belembu elicolekileyo bendlu kaAshibeya\x + 15.27.\x*,
\v 22 loJokimi, lamadoda akoKhozeba\x + Josh. 15.44.\x*, loJowashi, loSarafi ababebusa amaMowabi, loJashubi-Lehema. Lalezizindaba zindala.
\v 23 Labo babengababumbi, labakhileyo ezilimeni lezintangweni; bahlala lapho lenkosi emsebenzini wayo.
\s Inzalo kaSimeyoni
\p
\v 24 Amadodana kaSimeyoni: ONemuweli, loJamini, loJaribi, uZera, uShawuli,
\v 25 uShaluma indodana yakhe, uMibhisamu indodana yakhe, uMishima indodana yakhe.
\v 26 Lamadodana kaMishima: UHamuweli indodana yakhe, uZakuri indodana yakhe, uShimeyi indodana yakhe.
\v 27 Njalo uShimeyi wayelamadodana alitshumi lesithupha lamadodakazi ayisithupha; kodwa abafowabo babengelabantwana abanengi, losendo lonke lwabo kalwandanga njengabantwana bakoJuda\x + 4.38. Gen. 49.7. Nani 2.4,13. 26.14,22.\x*.
\v 28 Basebehlala eBherishebha\x + Josh. 19.2-8.\x* leMolada leHazari-Shuwali
\v 29 leBiliha\x + Josh. 15.29,30.\x* leEzema\x + Josh. 15.29,30.\x* leToladi\x + Josh. 15.29,30.\x*
\v 30 leBethuweli\x + Josh. 19.4,6.\x* leHorma\x + 1 Sam. 30.30.\x* leZikilagi
\v 31 leBeti-Marikabothi leHazari-Susimi leBeti-Biri\x + Josh. 19.4,6.\x* leShaharayimi\x + Josh. 19.4,6.\x*. Le yayiyimizi yabo kwaze kwaba sekubuseni kukaDavida.
\v 32 Lemizana yabo: IEtamu, leAyini\x + Josh. 15.32.\x*, iRimoni\x + Josh. 15.32.\x*, leTokeni, leAshani, imizi emihlanu,
\v 33 layo yonke imizana yayo, eyayiyizingelezele leyomizi, kuze kube seBahali. Lezi zindawo zabo zokuhlala, njalo baba lombhalo wosendo lwabo.
\p
\v 34 LoMeshobabi loJamileki loJosha indodana kaAmaziya,
\v 35 loJoweli loJehu indodana kaJoshibhiya indodana kaSeraya indodana kaAsiyeli,
\v 36 loEliyohenayi loJahakoba loJeshohaya loAsaya loAdiyeli loJesimiyeli loBhenaya,
\v 37 loZiza indodana kaShifi indodana kaAloni indodana kaJedaya indodana kaShimiri indodana kaShemaya.
\v 38 Laba abaqanjwe ngamabizo babeyizikhulu ensendweni zabo, lezindlu zaboyise\x + 4.27.\x* zanda kakhulu ngobunengi\x + Gen. 28.14.\x*.
\p
\v 39 Basebesiya ekungeneni kweGedori\x + 4.4,18. Josh. 15.58.\x*, baya ngempumalanga kwesihotsha, ukudingela imihlambi yabo idlelo.
\v 40 Bafica idlelo elivundileyo lelihle, lommango obanzi emaceleni\x + Hlab. 104.25.\x*, lolokuzola, lolokuthula\x + Hlu. 18.7,27.\x*; ngoba \add aba\add*koHamu babehlala khona endulo.
\v 41 Lalabo ababebhalwe ngamabizo bafika ensukwini zikaHezekhiya inkosi yakoJuda\x + 4.34-38.\x*, batshaya amathente lendawo zokuhlala ezazitholakala khona, babatshabalalisa kuze kube lamuhla\x + Hlu. 10.12.\x*; bahlala endaweni zabo, ngoba kwakukhona lapho idlelo lezimvu zabo\x + 5.22.\x*.
\v 42 Kwasekuphuma kubo, ebantwaneni bakoSimeyoni, amadoda angamakhulu amahlanu, aya entabeni yeSeyiri\x + Gen. 36.8.\x*. LoPelatiya loNeyariya loRefaya loUziyeli amadodana kaIshi babezinhloko zabo.
\v 43 Basebetshaya insali yabaphephayo bamaAmaleki, bahlala khona kuze kube lamuhla\x + 1 Sam. 15.2.\x*.
